Suzanne Vos bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa
Ọ bụ onye otu Inkatha Freedom Party na Parliament.
Vos bụkwa onye otu Pan-African Parliament na onye na-ekwuchitere Kọmitii na Transport, Industry, Communications, Energy, Science and Technology, otu n'ime Kọmitii ya na-adịgide adịgide
Vos nọ ugbu a na bọọdụ nke South African Broadcasting Commission (SABC).
